name: Career Transition (Onboarding) Toolkit
description: Starting a new job proper is crucial. Yet, many people may be unsure what to do or prep for in advance. This template serves to bridge that gap for young professional working adults who are looking for a system to consolidate what they need to know/do for a job transition into a new role or company.See video for details: Please make sure that you are comfortable with notion before purchasing.For any feedback, please reach out to me at cadence.csh@gmail.com.
